{"tid":861773,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"生產效益比中國高！Casio暢銷手錶生產線搬回日本","createTime":"2018-10-14T11:29:15.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-14T14:30:04.000Z","uid":39464,"like":29,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"9b36af7fb4454a17f786a50430f9e87f2730c562","tid":861773,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-14T11:29:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_php4Ig1Oe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_php4Ig1Oe.jpg&h=b2e08821&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕日本跨國的消費性電子產品和商用電子產品製造公司「卡西歐（Casio）」，決定將旗下暢銷手錶產品生產線搬回日本，採完全自動化生產，整體效益比給中國代工還要高。<br />\n<br />\n綜合日媒報導，卡西歐停止型號「A159WA」暢銷手錶之海外生產線，在2018年8月下旬啟動位於山形縣東根市的生產基地，以全自動化生產線製造該型號手錶，將原本14名作業員減低至5人，每人每日工時8小時，生產效率還提高3倍，製造成本降低50%，比請中國代工還划算。<br />\n<br />\n卡西歐型號「A159WA」暢銷手錶在日本國內售價約在1000至3000日元（約為台幣275元至826元），屬廉價手錶，從1989年上市以來已有近30年歷史，在全球銷售成績亮眼，尤以新興國家銷售量為佳；全自動生產後，原本工廠內的作業員轉為手工嵌產高單價商品。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2580530\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2580530&d=L6f164h82MN4k%2FTBwNsUBLIOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=e9950379\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2580530&h=049187f8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2580530</a>"},{"pid":"5bf78d73906dd6fbfc00a6e167ff1d50aea4b6a1","tid":861773,"uid":209487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-14T11:29:49.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c4f3546341ea75e4495250f407cee100ffa55ad9","tid":861773,"uid":209487,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-14T11:30:32.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6ec26cc68728839c883f899a77b8fbde632f853d","tid":861773,"uid":209487,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-14T11:31:33.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{